Name: Dungeon of Death
About the game: Dungeon of Death is a 3D adventure game with RPG elements.In which you will have to explore the dungeon and fight various monsters to find the necromancer who gave you eternal life.You will expect 14 game levels in which you will have to search for a portal to go to the next level in search of a necromancer, but do not think that this will be an easy task because the closer you are to your main enemy, the stronger the enemies will become. The main character is tired of the eternal life that the necromancer has endowed him with and decided to end it in order to finally retire, but he will have to go through a huge dungeon in which the necromancer lives, fight with many monsters that guard this dungeon, explore the dungeon to find weapons that will help fight,avoid traps, as well as solving riddles. Key Features : - Isometric 3D graphics with a touch of nostalgia - 14 different levels - Various enemies , many different weapons - Dark soundtrack
